|Description|

Battle arena stationed in space in the near future.

|ABOUT|

m4_arena is part of a series i will be making more maps for called "arena". Basically the map is layed out like an fy map but a little bigger. Both teams spawn with the same weapon. In this version the popular m4a1 rifle is used.

|Features|

-Explosive barrels
-underwater passages
-custom textures
